— In the Below Image we Can See All the 6 Tables which are Created Above has Relation Between Them.


customer_id is a Primary Key in the Customers Table and Foreign Key in the Orders Table


order_id is a Primary Key in the Orders Table and Foreign Key in the order_items Table


product_id is a Primary Key in the Products Table and Foreign Key in the order_items Table


category_id is a Primary Key in the Categories Table and Foreign Key in the Products Table


department_id is a Primary Key in the Departments Table and Foreign Key in the CategoriesTable




